title: 34: The Jump-Start Your Diet Episode
itunes:title: The Jump-Start Your Diet Episode
description: HAPPY NEW YEAR! It’s time to jump-start your diet, Hungry Girl style! In this episode, Lisa shows you how to start off the year right, with HEALTHY tips and tricks for a successful 2019! Discover Lisa’s eating plan picks -- like intermittent fasting and the Hungry Girl Diet -- plus the three lifestyle strategies you need to keep you on track! So pay close attention... This is THE episode to kickstart a healthy new year! [www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast](www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast)
